{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1250\deff0\deflang1045{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset238 Microsoft Sans Serif;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\f0\fs17 io.tmpfile ()\par
\par
Returns a handle for a temporary file. This file is opened in update mode and it is automatically removed when the program ends.\par
}

{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1250\deff0\deflang1045{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset238 Microsoft Sans Serif;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\f0\fs17 io.type (obj)\par
\par
Checks whether obj is a valid file handle. Returns the string "file" if obj is an open file handle, "closed file" if obj is a closed file handle, or nil if obj is not a file handle.\par
}

