\viewkind4\uc1\pard\f0\fs17 file:close ()\par
\par
Closes file. Note that files are automatically closed when their handles are garbage collected, but that takes an unpredictable amount of time to happen.\par
}

{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1250\deff0\deflang1045{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset238 Microsoft Sans Serif;}}
